          "reviewBody": "This is our first year in lexicon international school, really nice experience as a parent to see my kid presentation in front of audience in C2B,\nWith out stage fear he did the presentation this is all due to the efforts of teachers and management, the way of teaching the communication skills to kids was really awesome 👌\nThank you lexicon team",
