            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Lexicon Adventure Series.\nThank you Team Lexicon for the educational trip organized for the class 11th students. Our child Arianna  had an enriching experience n gained a lot of knowledge  through her visit to the Indian Air force Station.\nGreat efforts from all the teachers  who accompanied the students on this trip. Wonderful Initiative!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
