            "name": "Amruta Parkhe"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-05",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The Lexicon International School, Wagholi always comes up with  new ideas for students as well as parents.\n\nEarlier it was session for parents based on MR Script writing which was useful to improve child's way of writing and phonics session for development in reading.\nToday another session was for parents to understand our child's psychology and how to face their tantrums.  How to react to them . Well explained by Tonmoy Sir and Greeshma Ma'am. And solved our queries. Guided us well.\nA big thank you to the School, Principal Ma'am and the Team for arranging such a  helpful session.\nLooking for another session in future.\nBest wishes !!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
